Package de.feu.massim22.group3.map

Class Navi

java.lang.Object
de.feu.massim22.group3.map.Navi
All Implemented Interfaces:
Disposable, INavi, INaviAgentV1, INaviAgentV2, INaviTest
public class Navi extends Object implements INaviAgentV1, INaviAgentV2, INaviTest
The Singleton Class Navi acts as an entry point for getting information from the game map. Furthermore it manages the path finding process and the merge of different agent groups.
Author:
Heinz Stadler, Melinda Betz (contributor)

      lastActionSuccess - an indicator if the last action was successful
      lastActionIntention - the name of the intention the last action came from
      groupDesireType - the name of the group desire the agent has in its desires
      groupDesirePartner - the name of the team mate which performs a group desire with the agent
      groupDesireBlock - the block on which the group desire is based on
      attachedThings - a String containing information about the attached things of the agent

    • updateMapAndPathfind

      public PathFindingResult[][] updateMapAndPathfind(String supervisor, String agent, int agentIndex, Point position, int vision, Set<massim.protocol.data.Thing> things, List<Point> goalPoints, List<Point> rolePoints, int step, String team, int maxSteps, int score, Set<massim.protocol.data.NormInfo> normsInfo, Set<massim.protocol.data.TaskInfo> taskInfo, List<Point> attachedThings, List<Point> marker)
      Saves data from an agent received in the current step into the GameMap and starts path finding.
      Specified by:
      updateMapAndPathfind in interface INaviAgentV1
      Parameters:
      supervisor - the name of the supervisor of the group the agent is part of
      agent - the name of the agent
      agentIndex - the index of the agent
      position - the current position of the agent
      vision - the size of the vision of the agent
      things - the things which are currently in vision
      goalPoints - the goal points which are currently in vision
      rolePoints - the role points which are currently in vision
      step - the current step of the simulation
      team - the name of the team the agent is part of
      maxSteps - the number of steps the match has
      score - the current score of the team
      normsInfo - the current active norms
      taskInfo - the current active tasks
      attachedThings - the attached points of the agent
      marker - the marker which are currently in vision
      Returns:
      a two dimensional Array of type PathFindingResult which contains information about distance and direction of certain interesting points.
